race.comment: PREPOTENT (4) has a handy record over this mile journey with a win and two placings from just four attempts. Should get a cosy run in transit from gate three and looms as the main contender. SAND 'N' POWER (7) has strung two wins together on the bounce and is racing high on confidence of late. Likely to be in the finish again. BLAZERRO (3) gets the services of Wiggins in the irons and looks one for the exotics players. READY TIGER (5) is yet to miss a place in three starts over this track and trip and may trouble the judge with any luck in running. ACCLIMATISE (1) gets the claim and will give backers a sight up on speed.
